

    Open Projects from gluino.com and mdj.dk
    
    

    - tier3tools
        
        A series of small python executables, created to 
        ease communication with storage elements on the
        nordugrid.
        
    

	- config scripts

		A collection of various useful scripts
		
	- arc_setup_mac
	
		A set of setup scripts that will set the necessary
		environment variables that are needed so xrootd can
		use your arc-proxy.
		Assumes that the nordugrid-arc-nox client is installed:
		http://download.nordugrid.org/software/nordugrid-arc-nox/releases/1.2.0/